dataList.content: Dante, something about this containment unit seems different from the others, does it not?
<Yeah, it really does… Wait, is this―?>
Yes, that is most likely where we can find the Abnormality in which the Golden Bough has taken root.
Haah… We did manage to come this far, huh.

dataList.title: Grade 8 Fixer
dataList.content: …When we go back to the bus, can I teach Charon how to use a map?
…Yeah, sounds good. I’m sure she’ll like it.
Sinclair shook his head, then dry-retched afterward.

dataList.title: Grade 8 Fixer
dataList.content: Huhu, it’s nice to have a place to go back to.
